data.description: Discover the perfect blend of classic charm and modern comfort in this updated Cape Cod gem. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 1 bath, this home welcomes you with a timeless stone exterior. Step inside to find a seamlessly neutral decor, creating a canvas for your personal style. Every corner exudes warmth and character, making it an ideal haven for family gatherings. Don't miss the chance to call this inviting residence your home sweet home.
